Golden Arrows coach Steve Komphela may be known for his wizardry  on the pitch, but to his more than  73,000 Twitter followers, he also provides some insightful philosophical debate. Like on Tuesday, when Komphela posted a video of himself posing a question to fans about whether they would rather  buy a Toyota or a Rolls-Royce. The option, of course, came with a few conditions. He then spent a good portion of his night responding to comments from fans. Topics like losing  one's identity, the power of words and persistence dominated his TL. #Deep